// Personal Law (views/law/personal.pug)
extends ../layouts/main

block content
  .law-container
    .container
      h1 Personal Law
      .law-section
        h2 Step 1: What is Personal Law about?
        p Personal law governs matters related to individuals' personal affairs, including family, property, and personal rights. In India, personal laws are often based on religion and customs, covering marriage, divorce, inheritance, adoption, and maintenance.
        p This area of law includes property disputes, consumer rights, personal injury claims, and other individual legal matters. It encompasses both religious personal laws and secular laws applicable to all citizens.
      
      .law-section
        h2 Step 2: Why do we need Personal Law and Solutions?
        h3 Why We Need Personal Law:
        ul
          li Resolution of family and personal disputes
          li Protection of property rights and inheritance
          li Safeguarding consumer interests
          li Compensation for personal injuries
          li Maintenance of social harmony and justice
        h3 Solutions:
        ul
          li Legal representation in personal matters
          li Mediation and alternative dispute resolution
          li Proper documentation and evidence gathering
          li Understanding of rights and legal procedures
          li Timely legal action to protect interests
      
      .law-section
        h2 Step 3: Help and Description
        h3 Key Areas of Personal Law:
        .personal-areas
          .area-card
            h4 Property Disputes
            p Land, house, and property ownership conflicts
          .area-card
            h4 Consumer Rights
            p Protection against unfair trade practices
          .area-card
            h4 Personal Injury
            p Compensation for accidents and injuries
          .area-card
            h4 Family Law
            p Marriage, divorce, custody, and maintenance
          .area-card
            h4 Inheritance
            p Succession and will matters
        h3 Important Procedures:
        ul
          li Property dispute resolution through courts or tribunals
          li Consumer complaint filing under Consumer Protection Act
          li Personal injury claims and compensation procedures
          li Family court procedures for matrimonial matters
          li Will execution and succession procedures
        h3 Religious Personal Laws:
        ul
          li Hindu Personal Law (Hindu Marriage Act, Hindu Succession Act)
          li Muslim Personal Law (Shariat Act)
          li Christian Personal Law (Indian Divorce Act)
          li Parsi Personal Law (Parsi Marriage Act)
      
      .chatbot-section
        h2 Personal Law Chatbot
        .chatbot-container
          .chat-messages#chat-messages
            .message.bot-message
              p Welcome! I can help you with personal law queries. What would you like to know about property disputes, consumer rights, or personal injury?
          .chat-input-container
            input(type='text', id='chat-input', placeholder='Ask about personal law...', class='law-chat-input')
            button#send-btn Send